<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.5.9">
<l>maṉṉaṉṟaṉ tēvimār kaṇṭu makiḻveyta</l>
<l>muṉṉiv vulakiṉai muṟṟu maḷantavaṉ</l>
<l>poṉṉiṉ muṭiyiṉaip pūvaṇai mēlvaittu</l>
<l>piṉṉē yiruntukuḻal vārāyak kākkāy</l>
<l rend="indent">pērāyi rattāṉkuḻal vārāyak kākkāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Caw! Caw! Having placed the golden head of him,</l>
<l rend="indent">who long ago measure the entirety of this world</l>
<l rend="indent">so that, having witnessed [this], the wives of the king obtained joy,</l>
<l>on a bed of flowers, comb [his] curly hair at the back.</l>
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb the curly hair of he with a thousand names.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
